expected [Failed to Install] but found [LDAP
Having a single login for every service is a must in large organizations. This plugin allows you to integrate OrangeHRM with AD/LDAP quickly and easily.
Prerequisites:- ionCube Loader, ldap


Integration with Toggl
This addon allows you to Synchronise Toggl time entries with the OrangeHRM timesheets.
The Toggl Integration to the OrangeHRM application will allow users to seamlessly synchronise time entries on Toggl to the OrangeHRM system with a single click of a button. This would benefit the OrangeHRM user since there will be no duplication of work.

The add-on will be available with structured notifications being prompted on the OrangeHRM UI so that the user will be able to identify any message clearly which in turn would help in identifying the cause for the message.
Corporate Branding
Customize OrangeHRM to go with your organization's colors and themes. Have your company logo, banner and other color schemes integrated with OrangeHRM
Prerequisites:- ionCube Loader
Claim Plugin
The add-on for claim allows users to manage events and expense types, assignment of claims to employees, submission of claims for employees, and viewing of individual and employee claims.
Prerequisites:- ionCube Loader]
